    <item>
      <title>消费者名称中的“高低”方法：Leveille</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/-high-low-approach-in-consumer-names-leville-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Thornburg Investment Management 投资组合经理 Emily Leveille 在消费类股票中采取“高低”策略，偏爱 Brunelo Cucinelli 等超豪华品牌，而低端品牌则偏爱英国 B&amp;M 等品牌。她还看到许多从 GLP-1 药物转型中脱颖而出的赢家。她在“未平仓合约”节目中与彭博社的 Sonali Basak、Matt Miller 和 Katie Greifeld 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/-high-low-approach-in-consumer-names-leville-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:05:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
